                  <note>Marg. <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܕܐܒܪܗܡ ܢܦ̣ܬܪܝܐ ܐܝܬܘܗܝ</foreign>, "This is by <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/321">Abraham Nephtarenus</persName>." </note>
